   if(cphGlobal.getCookieByName('IsSubscriber') === 'True') {
        if(document.getElementById('adsense')) {
            document.write('<iframe width="1" height="1" src="https://www.pressdemocrat.com/ab-off-log/" style="position: absolute; left: -99999px;"></iframe>');
        } else {
            document.write('<iframe width="1" height="1" src="https://www.pressdemocrat.com/ab-on-log/" style="position: absolute; left: -99999px;"></iframe>');
        }
    } else {
        if(document.getElementById('adsense')) {
            document.write('<iframe width="1" height="1" src="https://www.pressdemocrat.com/ab-off/" style="position: absolute; left: -99999px;"></iframe>');
        } else {
            document.write('<iframe width="1" height="1" src="https://www.pressdemocrat.com/ab-on/" style="position: absolute; left: -99999px;"></iframe>');
        }
    }
  </script>

  <script id="tpl-story" type="text/template">
   <div class="story story-{{@index}}" data-tier="{{tier}}" data-hits="{{popHits}}" data-pub-date="{{dates.published}}" data-mod-date="{{dates.modified}}" data-pub-display="{{dates.pubDisplay}}" data-mod-display="{{dates.modDisplay}}" data-mod-text="{{dates.modText}}">
        <div class="story-inner" data-story-num="{{js '@index + 1'}}">
            <div class="story-thumbnail">
                <div class="story-thumbnail-inner">
                    <a href="{{href}}">
                        <img class="not-adapted" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" alt="{{image.alt}}" data-src-thumb="{{image.thumb}}" data-src-small="{{image.small}}" data-src-medium="{{image.medium}}" data-src-large="{{image.large}}" data-src-jumbo="{{image.jumbo}}" data-src-width="0">
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="story-copy">
                <div class="story-heading">
                    <h3><a href="{{href}}">{{headline}}</a></h3>
                </div>

                </div>

  </script>

        <div class="story-inner" data-story-num="{{js '@index + 1'}}">
            <div class="story-heading">
                <h3><a href="{{href}}">{{headline}}</a></h3>
            </div>
            <div class="story-thumbnail">
                <div class="story-thumbnail-inner">
                    {{#if video.embed.src}}
                    <iframe src="{{video.embed.src}}" width="100%">Your browser does not support iframes</iframe>
                    <div class="video-thumbnail-overlay">
                        <img src="https://img.pressdemocrat.com/shared/play-button.png" alt="play video">
                    </div>
                    {{else}}
                    <a href="{{href}}">
                        <img class="not-adapted" src="data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAAAAAP///yH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAIBRAA7" alt="{{image.alt}}" data-src-thumb="{{image.thumb}}" data-src-small="{{image.small}}" data-src-medium="{{image.medium}}" data-src-large="{{image.large}}" data-src-jumbo="{{image.jumbo}}" data-src-width="0">

  </script>
  <script id="tpl-video-image" type="text/template">
   <div class="story story-{{@index}}" data-tier="{{tier}}" data-hits="{{popHits}}" data-pub-date="{{dates.published}}" data-mod-date="{{dates.modified}}" data-pub-display="{{dates.pubDisplay}}" data-mod-display="{{dates.modDisplay}}" data-mod-text="{{dates.modText}}">

            <div class="story-thumbnail ratio-16-9">
                <div class="story-thumbnail-inner">
                    <iframe src="" width="100%" data-video-src="{{video.embed.src}}" data-video-ap="{{video.embed.autoplay}}">Your browser does not support iframes</iframe>

                        <img class="not-adapted" src="{{image.thumb}}" alt="{{image.alt}}" data-src-thumb="{{image.thumb}}" data-src-small="{{image.small}}" data-src-medium="{{image.medium}}" data-src-large="{{image.large}}" data-src-jumbo="{{image.jumbo}}" data-src-width="0">

  <script type="text/javascript">
   (function($) {
        $(document).on('click', '.video-thumbnail-overlay', function(e) {
            var iframe = $(this).parent().find('iframe').first(),
                apSrc = iframe.data('video-ap');

            iframe.attr('src', apSrc).closest('.story').addClass('video-is-playing');
        });
    })(jQuery);
  </script>

   {{#if stories}}
    <div class="block-template a1-container container" data-adapt-headlines=".a1-trending->.widget-area<=>.a1-impact->.widget-area">
        <div class="template-frame">
            <div class="template-content">
                <div class="template-content-inner clearfix">
                    <div class="a1-impact hed-700" data-stretch-headlines="2">
                        <div class="has-size-map image-stories" data-size-map='{"0" : "image-stories", "768" : "overlay-stories link-overlay hed-top", "1024" : "image-stories"}'>
                            {{#stories}}
                            {{#js_if '@index === 0'}}
                            {{> "impact"}}
                            {{/js_if}}
                            {{/stories}}
                        </div>

   {{#if stories}}
    <div class="block-template a1-container container" data-adapt-headlines=".a1-trending->.widget-area<=>.a1-impact->.widget-area">
        <div class="template-frame">

                            {{> "story"}}
                            {{/js_if}}
                            {{/stories}}
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="widget-area">
                <div class="widget-spacer">
                    <div class="widget-holder widget-centered"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="dark-heading m-top" style="background: #1361A4; margin-bottom: .35em; text-align: center;">NBBJ Events &amp; Nominations</div>
                <div id="a1-events"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

  <script type="text/javascript">
   templateMap.push({
        id       : 'a1-nbbj',
        slots    : {
            deDupe    : false,
            requireAll: false,
            hasWidget : 4,
            noWidget  : 4,
            reqImageIn: [0, 1, 2, 3]
        },
        layout   : {
            widgetCol: 'right',
            breakAt  : 1024,
            forceShow: true
        },
        callbacks: {
            success: function() {
                // pulls html from hidden div in HomeGrid2018
                var events = jQuery(this).find('#a1-events'),
                    placeholder = jQuery('#nbbj-events-calendar'),
                    firstDiv, secondDiv;

                if(placeholder.length) {
                    placeholder.find('script').first().remove();
                    firstDiv = placeholder.find('div[id^=cwwrapper_]');
                    secondDiv = placeholder.find('div[id^=cwucelist_]');

                    firstDiv.add(secondDiv).css({
                        position: 'relative',
                        top     : 0,
                        right   : 0,
                        bottom  : 0,
                        left    : 0,
                        height  : 'auto',
                        overflow: 'visible'
                    });

	                firstDiv.addClass('cw-outer');
	                secondDiv.addClass('cw-inner');

                    placeholder.find('td.cwuceeventtitle').css({
                        padding: '0 0 .8em'
                    });

                    placeholder.find('td.cwuceeventtitle > a').css({fontSize: '1em'}).wrap('<h3 style="margin: 0; line-height: 1.25; font-size: 1em;"></h3>');

                    placeholder.find('td.cwuceeventtitle > div[id^=eb]').css({
                        padding   : 0,
                        lineHeight: 1.3,
                        fontSize  : '.75em'
                    });

                    placeholder.find('td.cwuceeventtitle > div[id^=eb]').remove();

                    placeholder.find('td[id^=cwucebottomcell_] > a').each(function() {
                        var text = jQuery(this).text(),
                            first = text.substr(0, 1).toUpperCase();

                        jQuery(this).removeAttr('style').addClass('radius button').css({
                            background: '#1361A4',
                            height    : '1.5em',
                            lineHeight: '1.5em'
                        }).text(first + text.substr(1));
                    });

                    events.html(placeholder.html());

					var outer = events.find('.cw-outer');
					var inner = events.find('.cw-inner');

	                inner.css({
		                maxHeight: '400px',
		                overflow: 'auto'
	                });

					// if there is a scrollbar present
					if(outer.height() < inner.find('> table:first').height()) {
						outer.append('<div style="margin-top: .15em; font-size: .8em; line-height: 1.2; text-align: center;"><em style="color: #888888;">Scroll down for more events</em></div>');
					}
                }
            }
        },
        widgets  : [
            {
                size: 'cube',
                ads : [
                    {
                        view : 'phone,tablet,desktop',
                        size : [300, 250],
                        class: 'widget-cube'
                    }
                ]
            }
        ]
    });
  </script>

   {{#if stories}}
	<div class="block-template breaking-block-w-gallery container">
		<h4 class="block-heading dark-heading template-heading"></h4>
		<div class="template-frame">
			<div class="template-content">
				<div class="template-content-inner">
					<div class="template-spacer">
						<div class="featured-w-gallery-stories">
							{{#stories}}
								{{#js_if '@index === 0'}}
									<div class="featured-w-gallery-story fade-out-copy">
										{{> 'story'}}
									</div>
								{{/js_if}}
								{{#js_if '@index === 1'}}
								<div class="featured-w-gallery-image">
									<a class="featured-w-gallery-image-label" href="{{href}}">
										<i class="fa fa-camera"></i>
										Gallery
									</a>
									{{> 'partImage'}}
								</div>
								{{/js_if}}

  <script type="text/javascript">
   templateMap.push({
		id       : 'featured-plus-1',
		slots    : {
			deDupe    : false,
			countDupe : false,
			requireAll: false,
			hasWidget : 2,
			noWidget  : 2,
			reqImageIn: [0]
		},
		callbacks: {
			success: function() {
				var picked = $(this).find('.story-0'),
					head = picked.find('.story-heading'),
					updated = picked.data('mod-text');
				if(updated) {
					head.append('<p><small><em style="color: red;">' + updated + '</em></small></p>');
				}

				var parent = $(this).closest('[data-template="featured-plus-1"]'),
					type = parent.data('option') || '',
					label = parent.data('custom') || '',
					imageLabel = parent.find('.featured-w-gallery-image-label');

				if(type) {
					imageLabel.html('<i class="' + type + '"></i> ');
				} else {
					imageLabel.html('');
				}

				imageLabel.append(label);
			}
		}
	});
  </script>

                                {{#stories}}

  <script type="text/javascript">
   templateMap.push({
        id       : 'featured',
        slots    : {
            deDupe    : false,
            countDupe : false,
            requireAll: false,
            hasWidget : 7,
            noWidget  : 7,
            reqImageIn: [0]
        },
        callbacks: {
            success: function() {
                var picked = jQuery(this).find('.story-0'),
                    head = picked.find('.story-heading'),
                    updated = picked.data('mod-text');
                if(updated) {
                    head.after('<div style="margin: -.4em 0 .2em; padding: 0 .65em;"><p style="font-size: .85em; color: red;"><em>' + updated + '</em></p></div>');
                }
                jQuery(document).trigger('featuredBlockLoaded', [$(this)]);
            }
        }
    });
  </script>

  <script type="text/javascript">
   templateMap.push({
        id   : 'big-video',
        slots: {
            hasWidget : 7,
            noWidget  : 7,
            reqImageIn: [0, 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6]
        }
    });

    (function($) {
        // switch between videos in big-video block
        $(document).on('click', '.big-video-block .bv-alternate .story', function(e) {
            e.preventDefault();
            e.stopPropagation();

            var clicked = $(this),
                parent = clicked.closest('.big-video-block'),
                impactDiv = parent.find('.bv-impact .overlay-stories'),
                impactVideo = impactDiv.find('.story').first(),
                newAlternate = impactVideo.clone().hide().insertAfter(clicked),
                newImpact = clicked.clone().hide().insertAfter(impactVideo);

            clicked.fadeOut(180, function() {
                $(this).remove();
                newAlternate.show(0, function() {
                    $(this).removeClass('video-is-playing').find('iframe').attr('src', '');
                    smiBlock.adaptImages(parent);
                });
            });

            impactVideo.hide(0, function() {
                $(this).remove();
                newImpact.show().find('.video-thumbnail-overlay').trigger('click');
            });
        });
    })(jQuery);
  </script>

  <script id="tpl-g-carousel" type="text/template">
   {{#if stories}}
    <div class="smi2020-scg-block">
        <h2 class="smi2020-scg-block__heading smi2020-scg-heading__dark template-heading"></h2>
        <div class="smi2020-scg-block__carousel">
            <div class="smi2020-scg-block__carousel-button">
                <a href="/current-online-edition.html">View All Current Stories</a>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-container">
                <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                    {{#stories}}
                    <article class="swiper-slide">
                        {{> 'partImage'}}
                        {{> 'partHeadline'}}
                    </article>
                    {{/stories}}
                </div>
                <div class="swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white"></div>
                <div class="swiper-button-next swiper-button-white"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    {{/if}}
  </script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
   var gCarouselIncrement = 1;

    templateMap.push({
        id       : 'g-carousel',
        slots    : {
            deDupe    : false,
            countDupe : false,
            requireAll: false,
            hasWidget : 50,
            noWidget  : 50
        },
        callbacks: {
            success: function() {
                var thisId = 'g-carousel-' + (gCarouselIncrement++);

                jQuery(this).find('.swiper-container').attr('id', thisId);

                cphLoader.loadSwiper(function() {
                    var swiperContainer = jQuery('#' + thisId);
                    if(swiperContainer.length) {
                        new Swiper(swiperContainer, {
                            navigation     : {
                                prevEl: swiperContainer.find('.swiper-button-prev'),
                                nextEl: swiperContainer.find('.swiper-button-next')
                            },
                            loop           : true,
                            threshold      : 10,
                            effect         : 'coverflow',
                            coverflowEffect: {
                                slideShadows: true,
                                rotate      : 30,
                                stretch     : 4,
                                depth       : 100,
                                modifier    : 1
                            },
                            slidesPerView  : 5,
                            breakpoints    : {
                                599 : {
                                    slidesPerView: 1
                                },
                                1023: {
                                    slidesPerView: 3
                                }
                            }
                        });
                    }
                });
            }
        }
    });
  </script>
  <script id="tpl-carousel" type="text/template">
   {{#if stories}}
	<div class="smi2020-block__carousel">
		<div class="swiper-container">
			<div class="swiper-wrapper">
				{{#stories}}
				<article class="swiper-slide">
					{{> 'partImage'}}
					{{> 'partHeadline'}}
				</article>
				{{/stories}}
			</div>
			<div class="swiper-button-prev swiper-button-white"></div>
			<div class="swiper-button-next swiper-button-white"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	{{/if}}
  </script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
   var carouselBlockIncrement = 1;

	templateMap.push({
		id       : 'carousel',
		slots    : {
			deDupe    : false,
			countDupe : false,
			requireAll: false,
			hasWidget : 50,
			noWidget  : 50
		},
		callbacks: {
			success: function() {
				var thisId = 'block-carousel-' + (carouselBlockIncrement++);

				jQuery(this).find('.swiper-container').attr('id', thisId);

				cphLoader.loadSwiper(function() {
					var swiperContainer = jQuery('#' + thisId);
					if(swiperContainer.length) {
						new Swiper(swiperContainer, {
							navigation     : {
								prevEl: swiperContainer.find('.swiper-button-prev'),
								nextEl: swiperContainer.find('.swiper-button-next')
							},
							loop           : true,
							threshold      : 10,
							spaceBetween   : 2,
							slidesPerView  : 'auto',
							centeredSlides : true
						});
					}
				});
			}
		}
	});
  </script>
  <script type="text/javascript">
   Template7.registerPartial('story', document.getElementById('tpl-story').innerHTML);
    Template7.registerPartial('video', document.getElementById('tpl-video-image').innerHTML);
    Template7.registerPartial('impact', document.getElementById('tpl-impact').innerHTML);

    Template7.registerPartial('partImage', document.getElementById('tpl-part-image').innerHTML);
    Template7.registerPartial('partHeadline', document.getElementById('tpl-part-headline').innerHTML);
    Template7.registerPartial('partExcerpt', document.getElementById('tpl-part-excerpt').innerHTML);
  </script>
